Package: iotistica-agent
Version: DEB_VERSION
Architecture: DEB_ARCH
Maintainer: Iotistica <support@iotistica.com>
Installed-Size: DEB_SIZE
Recommends: docker-ce | docker.io | docker-engine
Section: net
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://iotistica.com
Description: Iotistica IoT Edge Agent
 Manages Docker containers, collects telemetry, bridges industrial
 devices (Modbus, OPC-UA, BACnet, SNMP, MQTT), detects anomalies
 locally, and syncs state with the cloud over MQTT.
 .
 Designed to run offline-first on Raspberry Pi and other edge hardware.
 Open the admin UI on port 48481 after installation to configure the
 device and optionally connect it to the Iotistica cloud.
